Online.ePayService for mobile devices

ePayService is a multifunctional payment solution for individual businesses and IT-professionals. Its user friendly interface and stylish layout meet the highest standards of the new generation of electronic payment systems and make the funds management simple and effective.

• TOP 5 for your business:
	– Online.ePayService wages settlement solution;
	– USD/EUR dual currency accounts;
	– Mass payments under affiliate programs;
	– Customized ePayService cards: add your company logo;
	– Virtual ePayService prepaid Single/Multi cards.

 • ePayService cards for your employees and partners:
	– Daily limit for ATM withdrawal and POS purchases up to 8500 EUR;
	– Instant free-of-charge load;
	– ATM withdrawal fixed charge of €1.99 only;
	– Possibility to manage card account using mobile device.

• Mobile-friendly version allows you to:
    - Replenish your ePayService card using iOS device
    - Initiate outbound and accept inbound transfers from other ePayServices users
    - Pay for mobile, internet and hosting services
    - Benefit from MasterCard:registered: live currency rates
    - Check current balance of your ePayService account in USD and EUR as well as the balance of your debit/virtual card account
    - Create a ticket in case if Support Team assistance is required
